Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.62,0:00:03.46,Teiko,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\fad(1400,900)}Teiko Middle School
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.80,0:00:06.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ナレーション）\N帝光(ていこう)中学 バスケットボール部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:05.62,CRKuro,NARRATOR,0,0,0,,The Teiko Middle School basketball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.43,0:00:09.04,CRKuro,NARRATOR,0,0,0,,Even amidst their brilliant record,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:08.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その輝かしい歴史の中でも—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.04,0:00:14.03,CRKuro,NARRATOR,0,0,0,,there was a generation of five prodigies \Nknown as the "Generation of Miracles."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:13.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10年に１人の天才が\N５人同時にいた“キセキの世代”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:16.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黄瀬(きせ)涼太(りょうた)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:16.14,CRKuro,NARRATOR,0,0,0,,Kise Ryota.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:17.82,CRKuro,NARRATOR,0,0,0,,Midorima Shintaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:17.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,緑間(みどりま)真太郎(しんたろう)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:19.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,青峰(あおみね)大輝(だいき)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.82,0:00:19.34,CRKuro,NARRATOR,0,0,0,,Aomine Daiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:21.10,CRKuro,NARRATOR,0,0,0,,Murasakibara Atsushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:21.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紫原 敦(むらさきばらあつし)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:22.37,CRKuro,NARRATOR,0,0,0,,Akashi Seijuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:22.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,赤司征十郎(あかしせいじゅうろう)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:30.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして\N彼らを脅かす誠凛(せいりん)高校の—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:33.17,CRKuro,NARRATOR,0,0,0,,They are threatened by Seirin \NHigh's shadow and light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:33.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,影と光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:21.24,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sensed it the first time we met.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:21.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黄瀬）初めて会ったときから\Nうすうす感じていた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:28.32,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,{\i1}After playing against him, \Nthat feeling crystallized.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:25.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦ってみて—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:28.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その予感は\Nくっきりと形を成し—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:32.92,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now it is total certainty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:33.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 完全に確信へと変わった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:39.51,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,{\i1}He is like us, the Generation of Miracles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:39.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつはオレたち\N“キセキの世代”と同種だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:44.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言わば オレたちとは\Nまったく違う道をたどった—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:46.72,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's a member of the Generation of \NMiracles that followed a different path.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:46.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“キセキの世代”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:50.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからこそ強く思う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:49.86,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I feel it so strongly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:51.88,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's instinct.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:52.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは本能だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:56.23,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to lose to him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:56.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつにだけは\N絶対 負けたくない！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:59.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（笠松(かさまつ)）切り替えろ\Nオフェンスだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:58.12,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,Change gears.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:02:59.61,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,We're on offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:01.37,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,Let's get them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:01.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取り返すぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:05.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってるっスよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:05.58,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:10.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黄瀬）そうだ 取り返す\Nぜってえ 負けねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:08.36,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. We'll get them back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:10.05,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,{\i1}We won't lose!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:17.05,EpTitle,EPTITLE,0,0,0,,Don't Underestimate Me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:24.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（火神(かがみ)）んん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:30.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黄瀬）フッ！\N（火神）えいっ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（火神）おっしゃー\N（黄瀬）なっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:32.77,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:34.52,CRKuro,KIYOSHI,0,0,0,,Nice, Kagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木吉(きよし)）ナイス 火神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:36.48,CRKuro,HYUGA,0,0,0,,Fast break!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:36.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,速攻！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:41.70,CRKuro,MURASAKI,0,0,0,,Wasn't Kise-chin's jump \Nway lower than normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:41.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紫原）今のは黄瀬ちん\Nいつもより全然低くない？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:49.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黄瀬）くそっ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:48.66,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:02.84,CRKuro,FAN A,0,0,0,,He made the shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:02.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（観客１）決まった！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:05.90,CRKuro,FAN B,0,0,0,,Kagami's crushing Kise in the ace battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:06.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（観客２）エース対決は\N火神が完全に押してる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:11.53,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not over yet. I can still fight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:11.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黄瀬）まだだ まだ戦える
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:14.28,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,{\i1}Failing now would be too lame!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:14.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな形で終わるなんて\Nダサすぎっスよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:17.83,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to lose to him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:17.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつにだけは\N絶対 負けたくない！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:21.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（オフィシャル）\Nメンバーチェンジ 黒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:21.53,CRKuro,REF,0,0,0,,Player substitution, black!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:25.74,CRKuro,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,Kise, you're out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:25.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（武内(たけうち)）黄瀬 交代だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:33.59,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,What? Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:33.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ？ ちょっ…\Nなんでオレなんスか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:34.63,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,If you sub me out now—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:35.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黄瀬）今 抜けたら…\N（笠松）黄瀬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:35.17,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,Kise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:38.38,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,Listen to the coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,監督の指示に従え
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:39.94,CRKuro,KIYOSHI,0,0,0,,A sub?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:40.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木吉）交代？\N（日向(ひゅうが)）まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:40.84,CRKuro,HYUGA,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:43.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黒子(くろこ)）黄瀬君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:43.30,CRKuro,KUROKO,0,0,0,,Kise-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:44.79,CRKuro,KAGAMI,0,0,0,,Kise...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:45.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（火神）黄瀬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:46.76,CRKuro,KAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:46.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（火神）やっぱり…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:48.47,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,It's your leg, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:49.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（笠松）足だな？\N（黄瀬）なっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:54.31,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,It's been bothering you since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:54.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（笠松）たぶん あんときからか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:58.97,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,You knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:59.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや… バレてたっスか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:02.99,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,You have to let me play, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:02.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど やらせてください
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:05.17,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,I can play through the pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:05.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなもん 気合でなんとか！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:07.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな形で負けるなんて\N絶対 オレは…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:07.78,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose like—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:12.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（笠松）なら こんな形に\Nしちまった時点で オマエの負けだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:12.79,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,Considering where we are, \Nyou've already lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.50,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:17.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オーバーワークが\Nオマエがそれだけ—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:19.62,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,I know you overworked yourself \Nbecause you were desperate to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:19.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ちたかったからってのは\N分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.12,0:05:23.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで痛めた足を\N灰崎(はいざき)にやられたことは—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:25.42,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,It was wrong of Haizaki to \Nstomp on your injured foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:25.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オレだって納得してねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:27.93,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,But that's not an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:27.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど それを言い訳には\Nできねえんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:31.93,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,It's all part of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:31.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうもん\N全部ひっくるめたのが試合だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:34.60,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,The game doesn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:34.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負には関係ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:38.96,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:39.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黄瀬）くそっ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:49.43,CRKuro,MORIYAMA,0,0,0,,You shut him down hard again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:49.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（森山(もりやま)）またずいぶんと\Nキツイこと言って引っ込めたな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:51.42,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:54.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（笠松）別に… これっきり\Nもう出られないほどのケガなら—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:54.54,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,If he were so badly injured \Nhe couldn't go on again,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:56.50,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,the coach never would've put him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:56.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,監督が初めから出してねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:59.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつは必ず戻ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:59.70,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,He'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:04.46,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,But we can't roll over \Njust because he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:04.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,が… いなくなったとたん\N戦えないんじゃ話になんねえぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.54,0:06:07.93,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,Show them what you're made of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:07.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意地見せろよ オメーら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.68,CRKuro,ALL,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:09.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海常(かいじょう)選手たち）おう！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:12.00,CRKuro,KIYOSHI,0,0,0,,This is our chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:11.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木吉）チャンスだな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊月(いづき)）ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:12.82,CRKuro,IZUKI,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:16.12,CRKuro,HYUGA,0,0,0,,We'll focus our attacks around Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:16.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日向）こっからは\N火神中心に攻めんぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.11,0:06:17.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（火神）うっす
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:16.87,CRKuro,KAGAMI,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:18.74,CRKuro,KUROKO,0,0,0,,Kagami-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:19.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黒子）火神君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:20.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:20.60,CRKuro,KAGAMI,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:22.70,CRKuro,KAGAMI,0,0,0,,I feel bad for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同情はある\Nだからこそ全力でやる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:24.82,CRKuro,KAGAMI,0,0,0,,That's why I'll play as hard as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:26.33,CRKuro,KUROKO,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:26.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:36.45,CRKuro,TSUCHIDA,0,0,0,,They're double-teaming him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:36.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（土田(つちだ)）ダブルチーム！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（中村(なかむら)）行かせない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.41,CRKuro,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,You're not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:43.52,CRKuro,HYUGA,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's Nakamura, a top eight \Nplayer in middle school!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:43.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日向）あいつ確か\N全中ベスト８の中村
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:45.84,CRKuro,HYUGA,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's famous for his defense!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:45.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ディフェンス力が有名な…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:48.01,CRKuro,HYUGA,0,0,0,,Kagami, pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:47.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日向）火神！ 出せ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:48.88,CRKuro,KAGAMI,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:49.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっす
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:53.51,CRKuro,KOGA,0,0,0,,All right! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小金井(こがねい)）よっしゃ 行けー！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:58.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（笠松）これは…\Nファントムシュート！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:58.64,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the Phantom Shot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:00.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小堀(こぼり)）ええい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:03.49,CRKuro,KOBORI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it! It's no use!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:03.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小堀）くそっ ダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:05.57,CRKuro,KOBORI,0,0,0,,{\i1}How does this shot even work?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:05.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうなってるんだ\Nこのシュートは!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.89,0:07:08.17,CRKuro,FUKUDA,0,0,0,,He made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:10.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（福田(ふくだ)）決まったー！\N（河原(かわはら)）２連続ゴール！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:10.28,CRKuro,KAWAHARA,0,0,0,,That's two baskets in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:12.32,CRKuro,HAYAKAWA,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:13.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（早川(はやかわ)）くっそおー すんません
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:16.24,CRKuro,HAYAKAWA,0,0,0,,Sorry! If I'd been guarding \Nhim more closely...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:16.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オエがもっとピッタイ\Nマークついてりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:20.26,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,You should be double-teaming Kagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:20.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや オマエ 今は\N火神のダブルチームだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:21.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカか オマエは!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:21.46,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,What are you, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.24,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,Besides, if you stick closer to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:24.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そもそもピッタリついたら—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:26.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よけい あのミス何とかに\Nかかりやすく…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:26.75,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,you'll only be more susceptible \Nto his mis-whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:33.09,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,I figured out why that shot disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:32.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かったぜ\Nあのシュートの消える秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:35.55,CRKuro,MORIYAMA,0,0,0,,Really, Kasamatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:35.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ 本当か？ 笠松
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:39.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ だが説明してる暇はねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:39.46,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I don't have time to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:42.31,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,Keep our current formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:42.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とりあえずフォーメーションは\N今のままでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:47.98,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,They'll have to bench Kuroko, \Nbut I won't let them do it for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:46.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐らく黒子は\N一度ベンチに下がる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:47.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,が ただじゃ帰さねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:52.26,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,I'll crush one of their weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:52.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,武器を１つ ぶっ壊してやる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:57.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（早川）えいっ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:07:59.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（早川）んぐっ…\N（森山･日向）リバン！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:07:59.41,CRKuro,BOTH,0,0,0,,Rebound!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:00.29,CRKuro,BOTH,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:03.86,CRKuro,KIYOSHI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crap.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:03.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木吉）しまった！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:05.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小堀）ぬうっ くぅ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:07.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ナイス バン！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:07.63,CRKuro,HAYAKAWA,0,0,0,,Nice rebound!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木吉）ううー うまい！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:09.63,CRKuro,KIYOSHI,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:12.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（森山）小堀！ 外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:12.80,CRKuro,MORIYAMA,0,0,0,,Kobori, outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:17.64,CRKuro,HYUGA,0,0,0,,{\i1}His form is still terrible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:17.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日向）やっぱフォームきたねっ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.25,CRKuro,FAN C,0,0,0,,He made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:21.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（観客１）入ったー！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:24.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（観客２）黄瀬がいなくても\N負けてねえ 海常！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:24.01,CRKuro,FAN D,0,0,0,,Kaijo's keeping up even without Kise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.52,CRKuro,MORIYAMA,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:26.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:31.67,CRKuro,KOGA,0,0,0,,Coach, isn't it time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:30.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カントク
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:32.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小金井）そろそろじゃね？\N（リコ）そうね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:32.44,CRKuro,RIKO,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:35.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（河原）あ 黒子の交代ですか？\N（リコ）そう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.44,CRKuro,KAWAHARA,0,0,0,,To sub out Kuroko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:35.91,CRKuro,RIKO,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:40.55,CRKuro,KAWAHARA,0,0,0,,But Kaijo's not handling Kuroko very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:38.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど 海常はここまで—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:40.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黒子に\N対応できてないみたいだし—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:41.87,CRKuro,KAWAHARA,0,0,0,,Couldn't he stay in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:41.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ このままでも…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:45.22,CRKuro,RIKO,0,0,0,,Kuroko-kun's just doing \Na good job avoiding them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:45.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは黒子君が\Nうまくかわしているだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:45.95,CRKuro,KAWAHARA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:48.79,CRKuro,RIKO,0,0,0,,His Misdirection isn't effective \Nfor as long against Kaijo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:48.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リコ）一度\N対戦している海常に—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:51.19,CRKuro,RIKO,0,0,0,,since we've played them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:52.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ミスディレクションの効果は短いし\Nそれが切れたら—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:54.81,CRKuro,RIKO,0,0,0,,Once that runs out, \Nhe'll only have his Overflow left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:54.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうオーバーフローしか\Nなくなっちゃうでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:56.47,CRKuro,KAWAHARA,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:59.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リコ）ていうわけで\N次のボールデットで交代よ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:59.26,CRKuro,RIKO,0,0,0,,So we'll sub him out the \Nnext time the ball's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:01.75,CRKuro,RIKO,0,0,0,,Mitobe-kun, get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:02.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,水戸部(みとべ)君 準備しといて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:05.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（氷室(ひむろ)）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:10.82,CRKuro,IZUKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's keeping his distance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊月）距離をとってる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:15.30,CRKuro,IZUKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if he's afraid of letting me \Nthrough, he's still faster than me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:15.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ペネトレイトを警戒するにしても\Nスピードはオレより上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:16.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:16.65,CRKuro,IZUKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:18.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木吉）伊月の\Nアウトサイドシュートは—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:20.33,CRKuro,KIYOSHI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Izuki's outside shooting \Npercentage isn't very good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:20.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確率が高くない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:22.87,CRKuro,KIYOSHI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he making him take the shot on purpose?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:22.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わざと打たせる作戦か？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:27.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊月）だとしたら打たない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:26.82,CRKuro,IZUKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I won't shoot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:30.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜなら\N火神に２人ついてる今—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:33.34,CRKuro,IZUKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}With two guys on Kagami, \Nthere's a more certain route we can take.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,より確実なルートが空いてる！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:36.36,CRKuro,KAWAHARA,0,0,0,,Go, Kuroko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:36.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（河原）よし行け 黒子ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:42.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊月）笠松!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.31,CRKuro,IZUKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kasamatsu?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:45.27,CRKuro,HYUGA,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this why he kept his distance from Izuki?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:45.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日向）伊月から距離をとったのは\Nこのため？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:50.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バックステップ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:50.48,CRKuro,HYUGA,0,0,0,,A step back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.93,CRKuro,HIMURO,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（氷室）そういうことか！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:59.09,CRKuro,HIMURO,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought the ball's trajectory was \Nhigh, but it's just the opposite.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:58.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（氷室）オレは以前 ボールの\N軌道が高い可能性を考えたが—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:05.21,CRKuro,HIMURO,0,0,0,,{\i1}The unique low form of the shot is the \Nsecret behind his disappearing shot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:02.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの独特のフォームによる\N打点の低さ—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:05.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それこそが消える秘密だったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:08.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通常のシュートの場合—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:10.22,CRKuro,HIMURO,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the case of a normal shot, \Nthe defender looks upwards.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:10.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ディフェンスの視界は\N上を向いている
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:16.73,CRKuro,HIMURO,0,0,0,,{\i1}But because he thrusts the ball out from \Nhis chest, the ball's position is low.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:15.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが胸元から押し出すように放る\N彼のフォームは—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:17.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ボールの位置が低い
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:19.57,CRKuro,HIMURO,0,0,0,,{\i1}The defender looks down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:19.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ディフェンスの視界は下を向く
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:24.60,CRKuro,MURASAKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}The rapidly rising ball \Nquickly flies out of sight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:22.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紫原）急上昇するボールは—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一瞬で視界から外れる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:28.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同時に火神への視線誘導を\Nかまされて—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:28.57,CRKuro,MURASAKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the same time, he misdirects the \Ndefender's attention towards Kagami,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:32.61,CRKuro,MURASAKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}making him lose sight of the \Nball as though it disappeared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:30.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ボールを見失った
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まるで消えたみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:38.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（氷室）だが跳ばずに１歩下がれば\N視界が広がる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:37.55,CRKuro,HIMURO,0,0,0,,{\i1}But stepping back instead of jumping \Nbroadens your field of view.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:41.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとは そこから追いつく\Nスピードがあれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:40.93,CRKuro,HIMURO,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you have the speed to block it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:46.54,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,You're in plain sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:46.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,丸見えだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:57.20,CRKuro,FAN E,0,0,0,,He stopped it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:57.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（観客１）止めたー！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.38,CRKuro,FAN F,0,0,0,,First it was Kise, now it's Kasamatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:10:59.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（観客２）黄瀬に続いて笠松も！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:02.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（早川）おおー\N（森山）笠松
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:03.05,CRKuro,MORIYAMA,0,0,0,,Kasamatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:05.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:05.14,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:10.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウソだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:10.21,CRKuro,KOGA,0,0,0,,You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:13.65,CRKuro,TSUCHIDA,0,0,0,,That shot beat Murasakibara...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:13.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの紫原を破った\Nシュートが…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:18.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木吉）しかも黄瀬と違って\N秘密を暴かれたうえで…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:17.72,CRKuro,KIYOSHI,0,0,0,,{\i1}And unlike Kise, he knows how it works.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:21.94,CRKuro,KIYOSHI,0,0,0,,{\i1}They've completely overcome the Phantom Shot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:22.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ファントムシュートは\N完全に攻略された
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:27.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（オフィシャル）\Nメンバーチェンジ 白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:27.58,CRKuro,REF,0,0,0,,Player substitution, white!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:33.45,CRKuro,KAGAMI,0,0,0,,Kuroko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:33.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（火神）黒子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:41.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黒子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:41.30,CRKuro,KOGA,0,0,0,,Kuroko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:45.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リコ）交代のタイミングが\N１歩遅かった…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:45.30,CRKuro,RIKO,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were late subbing him out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:49.75,CRKuro,RIKO,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now they'll think we subbed out \NKuroko-kun because they beat him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:50.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これじゃ 黒子君がやられて\N引っ込んだように見えてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.97,CRKuro,RIKO,0,0,0,,{\i1}It could affect our morale.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:52.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,味方の士気に響くかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:54.04,CRKuro,KUROKO,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:55.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黒子）すみません\N（リコ）おっ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:58.75,CRKuro,KUROKO,0,0,0,,My shot was blocked just \Nbefore I was subbed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.91,0:11:59.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,交代直前にブロックされて\Nしまいました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:01.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,流れを切ってしまって\Nすみません
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.61,CRKuro,KUROKO,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I made us lose control of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:03.18,CRKuro,KOGA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:04.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小金井）あれ？\N（土田）思ったより普通？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:04.82,CRKuro,TSUCHIDA,0,0,0,,His reaction is surprisingly normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:07.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小金井）\Nショックじゃないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:07.14,CRKuro,KOGA,0,0,0,,You're not shocked?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:11.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もちろん ショックです\Nけど 大丈夫です
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:08.98,CRKuro,KUROKO,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:11.00,CRKuro,KUROKO,0,0,0,,But it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.54,CRKuro,KUROKO,0,0,0,,Seirin hasn't lost the game yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:13.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ 誠凛が負けたわけでは\Nないですし—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:15.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:15.25,CRKuro,KUROKO,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:21.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（火神）黒子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:21.72,Flashback,KAGAMI,0,0,0,,Kuroko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:23.49,Flashback,KAGAMI,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:23.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,任せとけ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.75,0:12:27.43,CRKuro,KUROKO,0,0,0,,We have an ace we can count on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:27.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼れるエースがいますから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:31.39,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:37.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（笠松）今のダブルチームは\Nドライブを最も警戒していた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:39.72,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,{\i1}The double-team was trying to stop his \Ndrive, but he broke right through them?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:40.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その真ん中をぶち抜くだと!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:45.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うおーりゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:48.74,CRKuro,HYUGA,0,0,0,,K-Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:48.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,か… 火神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:51.84,CRKuro,KAGAMI,0,0,0,,Keep giving me the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:52.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（火神）ボール いつでもください\N（伊月）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:52.50,CRKuro,IZUKI,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:56.96,CRKuro,KAGAMI,0,0,0,,I feel like I can't lose right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:56.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか今 負ける気しないんで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:13.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（火神）えいっ\N（小堀）なっ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:16.53,CRKuro,FAN G,0,0,0,,He made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（観客１）決まった！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:19.98,CRKuro,FAN H,0,0,0,,Amazing! He tore right \Nthrough the double-team!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:19.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（観客２）すげえ\Nダブルチームを ものともしねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.29,CRKuro,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそっ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:23.04,CRKuro,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's extraordinary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:23.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（中村）切れが半端じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:26.45,CRKuro,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we're not careful, he could \Ninflict even more damage than Kise.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:26.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黄瀬と同じ…\Nいや下手したら それ以上じゃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:29.66,CRKuro,HYUGA,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:29.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やべえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:31.37,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,It's a three! Take the shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:31.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スリーだ 打て！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:33.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（森山）でえっ\N（火神）うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:34.38,CRKuro,MORIYAMA,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（森山）なっ 高すぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:36.00,CRKuro,MORIYAMA,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's way too high!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:39.25,CRKuro,KOGA,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:39.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小金井）行けー
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:45.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ パス!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:45.88,CRKuro,KOBORI,0,0,0,,What? A pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:55.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（歓声）\N（観客）ここで第２クオーター終了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:55.52,CRKuro,FAN I,0,0,0,,The second quarter is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:57.48,ScoreboardL,TEXT,0,0,0,,Kaijo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:57.48,ScoreboardR,TEXT,0,0,0,,Seirin
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:57.48,CRKuro,FUKUDA,0,0,0,,We're tied!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:57.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小金井）同点だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:14:00.19,CRKuro,KOGA,0,0,0,,We're back to square one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,振り出しに戻した
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:04.38,CRKuro,HYUGA,0,0,0,,How did you manage that pass then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:02.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日向）あそこで\Nナイスパスとか—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:05.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日向）何なんだ オマエは\N（火神）なんで？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:05.15,CRKuro,KAGAMI,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:08.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（森山）くっ\N（早川）ふんぎー！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.17,0:14:10.36,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,We're on break. Let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:10.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,インターバルだ 戻るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:20.29,Locker,TEXT,0,0,0,,Seirin High \NLocker Room
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:20.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リコ）みんな\N後半に向けてちょっと聞いて！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:20.29,CRKuro,RIKO,0,0,0,,Guys, listen up. Let's talk \Nabout the second half.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:22.98,CRKuro,RIKO,0,0,0,,I have nothing to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:23.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うことは… なし！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:24.48,CRKuro,ALL,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:25.50,CRKuro,RIKO,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:25.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リコ）ないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:28.22,CRKuro,KOGA,0,0,0,,But, Coach, you told us to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:28.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや カントクが\N“聞いて”って言ったんじゃん 今
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:31.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまりは順調ってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.57,CRKuro,RIKO,0,0,0,,It means things are going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:32.92,CRKuro,RIKO,0,0,0,,We'll keep playing like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後半も このままいくわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:36.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黄瀬君は足を痛めてるとはいえ—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:36.27,CRKuro,RIKO,0,0,0,,Kise-kun's foot is injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:38.23,CRKuro,RIKO,0,0,0,,but he'll definitely come back \Nbefore the end of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:38.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,終盤 必ずまた出てくるはず
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:41.69,CRKuro,RIKO,0,0,0,,We'll establish as much of a \Nlead as we can before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:41.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その前に リードを奪えるだけ奪う
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.68,CRKuro,RIKO,0,0,0,,Keep attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:44.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リコ）攻めあるのみ！\N（選手たち）おう！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:44.65,CRKuro,ALL,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:49.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黒子）火神君\N（火神）おう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.56,0:14:48.48,CRKuro,KUROKO,0,0,0,,Kagami-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:49.17,CRKuro,KAGAMI,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:53.91,CRKuro,KAGAMI,0,0,0,,Aomine's shoes are surprisingly comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:54.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,青峰の野郎にもらったバッシュも\N驚くほどしっくりきてる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:56.26,CRKuro,KAGAMI,0,0,0,,Let's go all-out in the second half.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:56.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（火神）後半も全開でいくぜ\N（黒子）はい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.26,0:14:56.62,CRKuro,KUROKO,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:15:00.25,CRKuro,KAGAMI,0,0,0,,Anyway, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:15:00.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それよか オマエのほうこそ\N平気なのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.99,CRKuro,KAGAMI,0,0,0,,They stopped your Phantom Shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:03.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ファントムシュート止められて\N何か 手はあんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:03.92,CRKuro,KAGAMI,0,0,0,,Do you have a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.74,0:15:06.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かりません
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:05.93,CRKuro,KUROKO,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:08.05,CRKuro,KAGAMI,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't you think you say that too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:08.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい！ オマエそういうの多くね？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:11.86,CRKuro,KUROKO,0,0,0,,But I don't have time to mope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:11.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど 落ち込んでばかり\Nいられません
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:14.85,CRKuro,KUROKO,0,0,0,,I have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:14.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何とかする…\Nしかないですね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:17.52,Locker Kaijo,TEXT,0,0,0,,Kaijo High \NLocker Room
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:17.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黄瀬）お願いします 監督！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.52,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,Please, Coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.52,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,Put me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:19.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オレを出してください
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:22.48,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who can stop Kagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:22.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,火神を止められるのはオレだけっス
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:23.69,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:23.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違うんスか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:26.28,CRKuro,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,No. The last two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:28.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだ ラスト２分\Nそこまでオマエを出すことはできん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:28.40,CRKuro,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,Until then, I can't put you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:31.53,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,But at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:30.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黄瀬）そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:31.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黄瀬）今のままじゃ…\N（森山）黄瀬！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:32.03,CRKuro,MORIYAMA,0,0,0,,Kise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:35.70,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,Moriyama-senpai, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:35.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黄瀬）森山先輩も\N何か言ってくんないんスか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:36.90,CRKuro,MORIYAMA,0,0,0,,Get...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:38.89,CRKuro,MORIYAMA,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Get on the court."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:40.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（森山）“出てくれ” 思わず\Nそう言ってしまいたくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.89,0:15:40.58,CRKuro,MORIYAMA,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish I could say it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:44.17,CRKuro,MORIYAMA,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're that powerless to \Nstop Kagami right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:44.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それほど今の火神は\N手がつけられない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:50.84,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,Kise...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:51.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黄瀬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:52.47,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:52.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:55.93,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,I understand your point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:55.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オマエの言い分は分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:02.10,ScoreboardL,TEXT,0,0,0,,Kaijo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:02.10,ScoreboardR,TEXT,0,0,0,,Seirin
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:02.12,CRKuro,REF,0,0,0,,The third quarter will now begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:02.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（オフィシャル）\N後半 第３クオーターを始めます
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:09.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（火神）やっぱり…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:10.07,CRKuro,KAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:15.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（笠松）オマエの言い分は分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:15.95,Flashback,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,I understand your point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:17.64,Flashback,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,But you still can't play.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:17.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが ダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:19.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黄瀬）な… ちょっ なんで…\N（笠松）うるせえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:19.39,Flashback,KISE,0,0,0,,What? Why can't I—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:19.95,Flashback,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.44,Flashback,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,That's an order, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:22.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先輩命令だ ボケ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:24.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１年が口答えしてんじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:24.96,Flashback,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,Don't talk back to me, first-year!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:28.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黄瀬）ホント\N体育会系っつうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:28.37,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's really spirited.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:30.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう言えば…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:34.98,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to think of it, he was \Nlike this when I joined Kaijo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:35.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海常 入ったときも\Nこんな感じだったっスね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.73,0:16:37.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ナガオカ）\Nナガオカショウヘイです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:37.34,Flashback,NEW MEMBER,0,0,0,,I'm Nagaoka Shohei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:38.63,Flashback,NEW MEMBER,0,0,0,,I'm from Iwai Middle School.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:40.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岩居(いわい)中出身 ポジションは\Nシューティングガード希望です
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:40.64,Flashback,NEW MEMBER,0,0,0,,I'd like to play the shooting guard position.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:43.11,Flashback,MORIYAMA,0,0,0,,Okay, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:43.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（森山）よし 次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:46.60,Flashback,KISE,0,0,0,,Me? Since I'm last, I'd better make it good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:46.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黄瀬）オレっスね\Nじゃあ せっかくのトリだし…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:49.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１年 黄瀬涼太っス
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:50.03,Flashback,KISE,0,0,0,,I'm first-year Kise Ryota.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:53.08,Flashback,KISE,0,0,0,,I play basketball for fun, \Nand I'm great at karaoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:53.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,趣味はバスケ 特技はカラオケ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:54.74,Flashback,KISE,0,0,0,,Wait, I mean the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:54.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 逆だった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:58.79,Flashback,KISE,0,0,0,,I'm from Teiko, and I'll play any position.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:56.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帝光中出身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:59.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ポジションは どこでもオッケー！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:01.69,Flashback,KISE,0,0,0,,I'll have to miss a lot \Nof practice since I model,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:04.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,モデルの仕事もやってるから\N練習あんま出られないかもだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:06.17,Flashback,KISE,0,0,0,,but I look forward to being on the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:06.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヨロシクッ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:09.13,Flashback,ALL,0,0,0,,Isn't he one of the Generation of Miracles?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:08.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部員）あれが\N“キセキの世代”の…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:11.30,Flashback,ALL,0,0,0,,He's a superficial idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:11.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（３人）そしてチャラい…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:14.12,Flashback,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:14.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（笠松）うるせえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:19.55,Flashback,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,I asked for your name, school, and position.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:19.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いたのは名前 出身校\Nポジションだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:25.86,Flashback,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,Just give me the answers I \Nasked for, you flashy moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:22.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いたことだけ—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.51,0:17:24.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハキハキ答えろや
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:25.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チャラ僧が！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:27.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黄瀬）いてっ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:27.35,Flashback,KISE,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:32.86,Flashback,KISE,0,0,0,,This is no way to treat the \Npromising rookie you scouted!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.51,0:17:30.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょ… スカウトされてきた\N期待のルーキーに—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:32.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この仕打ちは なくないっスか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:36.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知るか！ 先輩命令に\N１年が口答えしてんじゃねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:33.89,Flashback,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:37.07,Flashback,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,First-years shouldn't talk \Nback to their seniors!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:43.64,Flashback,KISE,0,0,0,,I don't like that kind of rigid thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:44.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黄瀬）苦手なんスよね\Nそういう堅苦しいの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:47.67,Flashback,KISE,0,0,0,,You think being a few years older \Nmakes you more important than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:47.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１〜２年早く生まれただけで\Nそんな偉いんすか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.57,0:17:52.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それにバスケもたぶん\Nオレのほうが うまいんスけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:52.67,Flashback,KISE,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm probably better at basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:58.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（笠松）偉(えれ)えよ\N（黄瀬）えっ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.58,0:17:57.64,Flashback,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,I {\i0}am{\i1} more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:58.26,Flashback,KISE,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:03.72,Flashback,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,Regardless of your skill, this is \Nthe Kaijo High basketball team.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:00.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,上手い 下手の前にまず—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.81,0:18:03.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここは海常高校\Nバスケットボール部だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:06.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早く生まれたからじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.53,0:18:06.67,Flashback,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,It's not because I'm older.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:12.61,Flashback,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,The second- and third-years have all worked \Nhard for this team for longer than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:08.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここにいる２･３年は—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:12.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな オマエより長く\Nこのチームで努力し 貢献してきた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:17.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのことに対する敬意を\N持てっつってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:17.05,Flashback,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to respect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:20.32,Flashback,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,I don't care if you're one of \Nthe Generation of Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:20.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“キセキの世代”だろうが\N関係ねえんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:24.65,Flashback,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,Now you're Kise Ryota, Kaijo first-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:24.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オマエはもう\N海常１年 黄瀬涼太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:28.56,Flashback,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,And I'm the captain, Kasamatsu Yukio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:28.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんでオレは ここの\Nキャプテン 笠松幸男(ゆきお)だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:33.41,Flashback,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,You got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:33.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か文句あんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:38.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黄瀬）威張ってるだけじゃ\Nないのは分かったけど—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:40.73,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it wasn't swagger, \Nbut I still didn't like it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:40.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,納得したわけでもなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:46.06,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I liked being "Kise of Kaijo."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:42.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ なんとなく—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:45.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“海常の黄瀬”ってのは\N気に入った
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:54.44,ScoreboardR,TEXT,0,0,0,,Kaijo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:00.53,ScoreboardL,TEXT,0,0,0,,Seirin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:07.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（歓声）\N（日向）よっしゃー
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:07.50,CRKuro,HYUGA,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:11.46,ScoreboardL,TEXT,0,0,0,,Kaijo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:11.46,ScoreboardR,TEXT,0,0,0,,Seirin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.80,CRKuro,KOGA,0,0,0,,We just keep scoring!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:11.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（福田）決まった！ 連続得点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.78,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:12.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそっ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:15.42,CRKuro,KISE,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please! Hang in there \Nuntil I can get back in!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:15.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黄瀬）頼む\Nオレが戻るまで何とか…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:17.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち着け 黄瀬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:17.36,CRKuro,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,Calm down, Kise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:19.94,CRKuro,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,You need to recover before \Nthe last two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:20.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残り２分まで回復に努めるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:24.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日向）まだ慣れねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:26.81,CRKuro,HYUGA,0,0,0,,{\i1}I still don't know when to block his shot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:26.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんてタイミングの取りづらい\Nシュートだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:39.12,CRKuro,HIMURO,0,0,0,,Kaijo's hanging on, but Seirin's \Nunstoppable right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:35.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海常も\N何とか追いすがってはいる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:39.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,が… 今の誠凛の流れは\N止められない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:42.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お返しだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:42.20,CRKuro,HYUGA,0,0,0,,Let's get them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:43.95,CRKuro,MORIYAMA,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyuga! A three?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（森山）日向 スリーか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:45.62,CRKuro,MORIYAMA,0,0,0,,No, you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:46.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（森山）させるか\N（日向）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:47.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日向）えいっ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:58.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小金井）ナイッシュー！ 水戸部\N（土田）連係 決まった！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:56.90,CRKuro,KOGA,0,0,0,,Nice shot, Mitobe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:58.52,CRKuro,TSUCHIDA,0,0,0,,Nice teamwork!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:06.18,CRKuro,HIMURO,0,0,0,,Even without Taiga, there isn't a single \Nplayer on Seirin they can leave unguarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:02.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（氷室）タイガは もちろん—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:06.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もはや誠凛には１人として\Nフリーにできる選手はいない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:08.68,CRKuro,HIMURO,0,0,0,,What will Kaijo do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:08.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうする海常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:11.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このままいくぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:11.85,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,Let's keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:13.56,CRKuro,MORIYAMA,0,0,0,,Kasamatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:13.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,笠松
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:16.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（早川）けど 火神はどうっす？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:16.59,CRKuro,HAYAKAWA,0,0,0,,But what about Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:19.79,CRKuro,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,I hate to admit it, but not \Neven double-teaming him works.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:20.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悔しいが今のヤツは\Nダブルチームでも…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:25.70,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,We expected this the moment \Nwe learned about Kise's foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:23.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（笠松）黄瀬の足のことを\N知ったときから—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この状況は想定してた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:32.29,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,But we weren't expecting \Nhim to grow so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:28.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただし想定外だったのは—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:32.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつの驚異的な成長速度だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:38.07,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,There's no good way for us to \Nhandle all five Seirin players.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:35.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 誠凛５人に\Nもれなく対応できる—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:38.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,都合のいい策はねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:40.26,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,But we can still score.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 点は取れる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:43.97,ScoreboardL,TEXT,0,0,0,,Kaijo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:43.97,ScoreboardR,TEXT,0,0,0,,Seirin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:43.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やるだけやって点を取られたら\Nしょうがねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.86,0:20:43.97,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,We'll do everything we can, \Nbut we can't help it if they score.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:46.66,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,But we will get them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:46.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただし 必ず取り返す！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:48.51,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,Stick to them like your life depends on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:48.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んでも食らいつくぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:49.93,CRKuro,ALL,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:58.02,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sound pathetic. I hate it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:57.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（笠松）ったく われながら\N情けねえ話だ ムカつくぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:01.86,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're desperately hanging on, \Nand Kise's our last hope.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:21:01.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必死でこらえて\N黄瀬が頼みの綱とはよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:06.57,CRKuro,KASAMATSU,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I'll happily do it if it means we'll win!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:06.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが それでも勝つためなら\N喜んでやってやるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:17.60,CRKuro,HYUGA,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's fast!{\i0}
